# CODEOWNERS requests review. It does not grant merge authority, prove
# specialist independence, or replace the requirements in MAINTAINERS.md.
#
# Current ownership is assigned to the sole active maintainer. Sensitive
# normative changes still require a qualified reviewer who is not the author.
#
# GitHub uses the last matching pattern. Broad collection ownership therefore
# appears before sensitive and contract-specific overrides.

